TELEMETRY SOURCE CONFIGURATION
------------------------------

The application consumes telemetry from F1 25 via local UDP broadcast.

Default configuration (Codemasters standard):

- UDP Protocol Version: 2025
- Update Rate: 60 Hz
- IP Address: 127.0.0.1
- UDP Port: 20777

All parameters are configurable via configuration files. The system assumes
local-only telemetry capture.

